l\">civil</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/administrator\" title=\"administrator\">administrators</a> and the <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/martial\" title=\"martial\">martial</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/office\" title=\"office\">office</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/holder\" title=\"holder\">holders</a>)"},{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/group\" title=\"group\">group</a> (of <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/people\" title=\"people\">people</a> doing the same <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/work\" title=\"work\">work</a>); <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/band\" title=\"band\">band</a>; <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/board\" title=\"board\">board</a>; <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/squad\" title=\"squad\">squad</a>; <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/committee\" title=\"committee\">committee</a>"},{"definition":"<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/shift\" title=\"shift\">shift</a>; <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/work\" title=\"work\">work</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/period\" title=\"period\">period</a>"},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt116\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/time\" title=\"time\">time</a> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/period\" title=\"period\">period</a>; <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/section\" title=\"section\">section</a> of the <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/day\" title=\"day\">day</a>"},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt117\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> (<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/college\" title=\"college\">college</a>-<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/level\" title=\"level\">level</a>) <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/subject\" title=\"subject\">subject</a>; (<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/academic\" title=\"academic\">academic</a>) <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/department\" title=\"department\">department</a>"}]}]